## DeepPropsObject type

Constructs an object with deep propeties TPath with value types from TObject

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type DeepPropsObject<TObject, Path extends string> = {
    [P in Path]: DeepPropType<TObject, P, never>;
};
```
